text: Claude Jean-Prost (20 November 1936 - 8 January 2018) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2018 deaths Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Jura (department)
